          { "feature": "duration_greater_15_min", "weight": 5 },
          { "feature": "recurrent_within_24h", "weight": 4 }
        ],
        "management": "Consider LP to rule out meningitis. Urgent EEG. MRI brain if focal features. No long-term AED. Counsel on slightly higher risk of later epilepsy."
